  "prompt": "What are some small restaurant chains in Dallas? (under 10 locations)",
  "response": "Here are some small restaurant chains in Dallas that have fewer than 10 locations:\n\n1. **Velvet Taco** - Known for its creative and globally-inspired tacos.\n2. **Twisted Root Burger Co.** - Famous for its gourmet burgers and quirky atmosphere.\n3. **Malibu Poke** - Offers high-quality poke bowls with a variety of fresh ingredients.\n4. **Grub Burger Bar** - Features inventive burgers and a lively atmosphere.\n5. **Meso Maya** - Specializes in authentic Mexican cuisine with a focus on fresh ingredients and traditional techniques.\n6. **Pie Tap Pizza Workshop + Bar** - Offers artisanal pizzas and craft beers in a casual setting.\n7. **Liberty Burger** - Known for its gourmet burgers and commitment to using high-quality ingredients.\n8. **Taco Joint** - A popular spot for tacos and Tex-Mex fare.\n\nThese chains are well-loved by locals and often have a strong community presence.",
